1.for changing the BANNER NAME we should download the primary boot loader file from git hub.

https://github.com/rugged-board/at91bootstrap-rba5d2x
 
2.after downloading from the github extract the zip file.

3.Go to the at91bootstrap folder and enable the Toolchain. 

4. Give the below commands :
 
 make mrproper.

5.After give the defconifg command :at91bootstrap-rba5d2x

make rugged_board_a5d2xsd1_uboot_defconfig

6. here there are 2 types options for menuconifg.

   1.vi .config   2.make menuconfig

open the menuconfig for GUI representation.

open the vi .config for text representation.

7. Go to the Hardware Initialization Options and 

CONFIG_HW_BANNER="\"\\n\\nAT91Bootstrap \" AT91BOOTSTRAP_VERSION \" (\" COMPILE_TIME \")\\n\\n\""

edit the banner name here and save the file.

8.Give the Cmmand for making the Image.

make 

and if we dont get any errors while building the image then the iamge is succesfully built.

9. the Image will be stored in the at91bootstrap/binaries 

10. Copy the at91bootstrap.bin image and copy to the BOOT FOLDER and test the image check the banner name in primary boot loader.
